{"tid":2100024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《國安法》成功平息動亂","createTime":"2020-07-08T17:15:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T20:08:11.000Z","uid":89160,"like":8,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b184358a9f7d9aeb44d71e92e8d431ff0376af75","tid":2100024,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:15:22.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"orange\"><strong>《國安法》成到測試到暴徒既底線</strong></span>，已經有黑暴討論「街頭抗爭歷史使命完成」，証明《國安法》精準打擊港獨勢頭。<br />\n<br />\n街頭回復和平，外國勢力干預失去著力點，縱使我方跟美帝仍然要堅持鬥爭，預計美帝不會就此罷休，但<strong><span class=\"orange\">香港再唔會係風暴中心，唔會集中制裁、干預香港事務，黑暴影響力自然減退，暴徒一係噤聲，一係諗移民，有利大局，香港再出發！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n多謝國安公署，多謝林鄭特首，多謝習主席！"},{"pid":"18a71e54edb4ffe6ddcbbfecb95d1265b7de677e","tid":2100024,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:19:02.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"orange\">天地有正氣  暴徒退散</span></strong></p><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZSDN2fX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZSDN2fX.jpg&h=6625025f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</p>"},{"pid":"4d3b3ab2f791ef4c49fb83607483bf3ef24bcdbc","tid":2100024,"uid":143343,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:20:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"740160933b10d7751cae55437d3d68168c865f8e","tid":2100024,"uid":273703,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:21:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"826f1963dea74df16a4f13a12b7a5a46254512f7","tid":2100024,"uid":89160,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:22:42.000Z","msg":"《國安法》最終目的就係要畀黑暴知道<strong><span class=\"orange\">烏合之眾難敵我人民政府，知難而退</span></strong>，習主席英明。"},{"pid":"3533dcec8a55ae5c9c17592637d9d41bdf810ac6","tid":2100024,"uid":80356,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:22:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xMdVrJN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxMdVrJN.jpg&h=4861a48d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7945e56b2822703ce1662a080bdcfd5fce527a11","tid":2100024,"uid":14494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:24:38.000Z","msg":"好似仲過埋外國底線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a0ee1b1f218c5ede2087b915cb2bed09d979d0","tid":2100024,"uid":89160,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"740160933b10d7751cae55437d3d68168c865f8e","tid":2100024,"uid":273703,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:21:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:29:56.000Z","msg":"我國以法律換取時間，香港動亂平息，起碼少左煩亂，我國就可以專心處理水災，積極備戰。咁亦係撕破西方既假面具，市面回復正常，西方再無籍口加強制裁，最多搞搞移民配額。<br />\n<br />\n事實只要市面回復平靜，我港居民自然回復信心，唔會咁多人移民，搞事者都逃亡西方，香港人安居樂業。"},{"pid":"5861a7aca40b70ca5a45c32d6e106c053cff2a96","tid":2100024,"uid":89160,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7945e56b2822703ce1662a080bdcfd5fce527a11","tid":2100024,"uid":14494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:24:38.000Z","msg":"好似仲過埋外國底線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:34:09.000Z","msg":"過左「底線」又如何？我地有底氣，有決心！<br />\n我預計西方亡我之心不死，但係就唔會再集中香港攻擊，減少不必要的戰場，香港情勢大好。"},{"pid":"84fdedb7f0d574a277db1b9c274a3afe4d27ba57","tid":2100024,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EjuBbe1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEjuBbe1.jpg&h=1c4484b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"314cadc5f6407c75487f0102899e5c60f3cbb638","tid":2100024,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:37:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b25d988d87226194d97c34d8679055a49e0f5e0c","tid":2100024,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:39:19.000Z","msg":"on99"},{"p