2280e103b93f18c8c14f54511b3b3b","tid":2100024,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:08:27.000Z","msg":"冇人上街，因為大家準備移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國又成為最後大贏家，不過得返個冇人冇錢既空港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d265b3122b15010ed9abcbfc34151bfdf06d1b","tid":2100024,"uid":89160,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"94855600c32280e103b93f18c8c14f54511b3b3b","tid":2100024,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:08:27.000Z","msg":"冇人上街，因為大家準備移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國又成為最後大贏家，不過得返個冇人冇錢既空港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:16:28.000Z","msg":"黑暴只係少數，移民只係皮毛<br />\n<br />\n更重要係令中產明白暴亂平息，只要不觸法就安全，加上西方經濟不景，只要有理性既人，我都好有信心沉默的大多數會留港建港！<br />\n<br />\n國安法令街頭回復平靜，既可以為習主席添功，亦可以減慢西方干預速度，佢地掛住移民反而畀到信心「沉默的大多數」，有助打消移民念頭！<br />\n<br />\n可以話係錯有錯著！惡有惡報！"},{"pid":"491c8e0ce4d62f6d20a0784a6b5c7d853a0eaba3","tid":2100024,"uid":89160,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:23:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"orange\">黑暴知難而退，市面和平，沈默大多數自然願意留港，你估移民真係你班黑暴諗得咁易？邊個捨得香港份工、香港朋友、香港娛樂？市面無事無幹邊個會走？證明黑暴都係自作聰明！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"701b193132f853c65904d272039cb1a96add17e8","tid":2100024,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"826f1963dea74df16a4f13a12b7a5a46254512f7","tid":2100024,"uid":89160,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:22:42.000Z","msg":"《國安法》最終目的就係要畀黑暴知道<strong><span class=\"orange\">烏合之眾難敵我人民政府，知難而退</span></strong>，習主席英明。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T18:51:42.000Z","msg":"輸了....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd05f3dddbf7530ed19c654aa0d6262fdfa1da7f","tid":2100024,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":1